<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Session Accepted</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #2461CB;
            padding: 10px;
            color: white;
        }
        .details {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background-color: #2461CB;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Session Accepted!</h1>
        </div>
        <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>
        <p>Great news! The artist <strong><%= artistName %></strong> has accepted your session request. Here are the details:</p>
        
        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>Booking Date:</strong> <%= bookingDate %></p>
            <p><strong>Booking Time:</strong> <%= bookingTime %></p>
        </div>

        <p>We look forward to seeing you at the session. If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>

        <p>Thanks,<br/>Zinkly</p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
            <a href="<%= bookingLink %>" target="_blank" class="button">Join Session</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>